OL,3,CSunak hints he could cut benefits to
OL,4,Cfund plan to scrap National Insurance
OL,6,FIn an interview with the Sunday Times,
OL,7,FMr Sunak set out his intention to
OL,8,Fconsult on new plans to reduce working-
OL,9,Fage benefits "to make sure that we can
OL,10,Fsustainably keep cutting taxes".
OL,11,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt used his Budget
OL,12,Fto set out a 2p cut in National
OL,13,FInsurance from April with a vague
OL,14,Fpromise to eventually deliver a
OL,15,Fsimpler tax system by eventually
OL,16,Fgetting rid of it altogether.JMr Sunak
OL,17,Fstressed his commitment to ending the
OL,18,F"unnecessarily complex" system of
OL,19,Fhaving both income tax and National
OL,20,FInsurance contributions (NICs).
