OL,3,CSunak hints he could cut benefits to
OL,4,Cfund plan to scrap National Insurance
OL,6,F"All that money ultimately goes into
OL,7,Fthe same pot to fund public services,"
OL,8,Fthe prime minister said.
OL,10,F"So ... our long-term ambition is to
OL,11,Fend that unfairness, to keep cutting
OL,12,FNICs until it's gone, because that is
OL,13,Fthe best way to reward hard work,
OL,14,Fsimplify the tax system, and build the
OL,15,Fkind of society that I think is right."
